from the cabin.

00:01:34.030 --> 00:01:39.300
In the fall, the nearby Salmon Viewing Area
provides opportunities to view the amazing

00:01:39.300 --> 00:01:42.520
fish from the interpretive boardwalk.

00:01:42.520 --> 00:01:51.140
We remind visitors to the Boise National Forest
that reservations can be made at www.recreation.gov

00:01:51.140 --> 00:01:59.299
or by calling 1-877-444-6777.

00:01:59.299 --> 00:02:08.619
Further information is also available by calling
the Forest Service at area code 208-373-4007.

